OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775059860
OL,3,CChancellor promises help is coming -
OL,4,Cbut not yet, and not for everyone
OL,6,FThe chancellor has promised people
OL,7,Fwill get help with their energy bills,
OL,8,Fwhich are being driven up by the Iran
OL,9,Fwar, but support isn't coming yet, and
OL,10,Fit won't be for everyone.
OL,12,FHousehold energy bills have fallen on
OL,13,FWednesday by 7% thanks to the latest
OL,14,Fprice cap, but they are expected to
OL,15,Frise by 18% hike from July.
OL,17,FRachel Reeves told ITV News she is
OL,18,Fusing a three-month delay between
OL,19,Fprice caps, when warm weather means
OL,20,Fenergy consumption is lower, to assess
OL,21,Fwhat support could be provided.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775059860
OL,3,CChancellor promises help is coming -
OL,4,Cbut not yet, and not for everyone
OL,6,F"We're using this time we have to work
OL,7,Fthrough all the different
OL,8,Fcontingencies and different options,
OL,9,Ffor more tailored and targeted support.
OL,11,F"What we've done so far is reducing
OL,12,Fcosts for everybody's prescriptions,
OL,13,Ftrains, and of course, most of all on
OL,14,Fenergy bills," she said. "But we're
OL,15,Flooking at what else might be needed."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775059860
OL,3,CChancellor promises help is coming -
OL,4,Cbut not yet, and not for everyone
OL,6,FHer words come ahead of a press
OL,7,Fconference by Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer, where he set out plans to
OL,9,Fdeal with the ongoing conflict in the
OL,10,FMiddle East and government support for
OL,11,Fhouseholds.
OL,13,FSince fighting began in Iran, oil
OL,14,Fprices have soared in response to
OL,15,FTehran's block on tankers passing
OL,16,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,18,FFamilies with a 55-litre diesel car
OL,19,Fface paying more than #100 at the pump
OL,20,Ffor the first time since December 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775059860
OL,3,CChancellor promises help is coming -
OL,4,Cbut not yet, and not for everyone
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FBut the chancellor said she was
OL,12,Fholding off making any decision on
OL,13,Fwhether to scrap a planned 1p rise in
OL,14,Ffuel duty, which is set for September.
OL,16,F"At the moment it's difficult to know
OL,17,Fwhere we're going to be in a week's
OL,18,Ftime, let alone in six months time, "
OL,19,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775059860
OL,3,CChancellor promises help is coming -
OL,4,Cbut not yet, and not for everyone
OL,6,F"So we're working through, different
OL,7,Foptions at the moment and to plan for
OL,8,Fdifferent eventualities."
OL,10,FShe added: "What we don't want to do
OL,11,Fis to have a sort of blanket approach
OL,12,Fof support during times of elevated
OL,13,Fprices, because all that means is that
OL,14,Fthe same people will have to pay back
OL,15,Fthat support with higher taxes, or
OL,16,Fless money for services like the NHS
OL,17,Fin the future.
OL,19,F"That's why at the moment we're
OL,20,Fworking on contingency planning and
OL,21,Ftailored, targeted support."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775059860
OL,3,CChancellor promises help is coming -
OL,4,Cbut not yet, and not for everyone
OL,6,FShe said the best way to get bills
OL,7,Fdown is to de-escalate the conflict in
OL,8,FIran and open the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,9,Fwhich is a critical shipping lane for
OL,10,Fmoving oil from the Persian Gulf.
OL,12,FIn normal times, the Strait would see
OL,13,Faround 20% of the world's oil supply
OL,14,Fflow through it, but that has been
OL,15,Freduced to almost zero since the
OL,16,Fconflict began.
OL,18,FReeves, however, insisted the UK has a
OL,19,Fsufficient supply of fuel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775059860
OL,3,CChancellor promises help is coming -
OL,4,Cbut not yet, and not for everyone
OL,6,F"We don't have a problem with supply.
OL,7,FThere's plenty of supply. The impact
OL,8,Fat the moment is a price impact.
OL,10,F"We get very little of our oil and gas
OL,11,Ffrom the Middle East, but we are all
OL,12,Faffected when prices go up."
OL,14,FAsked if people should ration their
OL,15,Fenergy usage, she said: "People
OL,16,Fshouldn't have those concerns. They
OL,17,Fshould carry on acting as normal. And
OL,18,Fthey should also be confident that
OL,19,Fgovernment is contingency planning for
OL,20,Fa whole range of scenarios."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775059860
OL,3,CChancellor promises help is coming -
OL,4,Cbut not yet, and not for everyone
OL,6,FShe pointed to action to prevent
OL,7,Fenergy bills unfairly profiting from
OL,8,Fthe crisis by price gouging, and said
OL,9,Fpeople looking for cheaper fuel can
OL,10,Fuse a government service to compare
OL,11,Fpump prices.
OL,13,FRAC figures on Tuesday showed average
OL,14,Fdiesel prices at UK forecourts were
OL,15,F182.8p per litre, up 40p since the
OL,16,Fstart of the conflict, which brought
OL,17,Fthe cost of filling up a 55-litre
OL,18,Ffamily car to #100.52.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775059860
OL,3,CChancellor promises help is coming -
OL,4,Cbut not yet, and not for everyone
OL,6,FThe average cost of petrol is 152.8p
OL,7,Fper litre, an increase of 20p since
OL,8,Fthe war began.
OL,10,FAhead of his press conference, the
OL,11,Fprime minister said: "In an uncertain
OL,12,Fand volatile world, it is my
OL,13,FGovernment's duty to protect the
OL,14,FBritish people at home and abroad.
OL,16,F"I know the public are concerned about
OL,17,Fthe conflict in Iran and what it means
OL,18,Ffor them and their families.
OL,26,@sD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775059860
OL,3,CChancellor promises help is coming -
OL,4,Cbut not yet, and not for everyone
OL,6,F"I want to reassure them that they
OL,7,Fhave a government on their side,
OL,8,Fworking with allies on de-escalation
OL,9,Fand bearing down on the cost of living.
OL,11,F"Today, millions of people up and down
OL,12,Fthe country will see energy bills go
OL,13,Fdown by #117, wages go up for the
OL,14,Flowest paid, and more support will be
OL,15,Favailable for people who need it most
OL,16,F` because of the decisions this
OL,17,FGovernment has taken.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775059860
OL,3,CChancellor promises help is coming -
OL,4,Cbut not yet, and not for everyone
OL,6,F"But we must go further to bear down
OL,7,Fon costs, and that means pushing for
OL,8,Fde-escalation in the Middle East and a
OL,9,Fre-opening of the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,10,FThat is the best way we can bring down
OL,11,Fthe cost of living for families and
OL,12,Fthat is my focus."
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
